complete.title: A new website logo was generated!

competion.prompt: the prompt(s) to generate completions for, encoded as a string, array of strings, array of tokens, or array of token arrays.
competion.max_tokens: the maximum number of tokens to generate in the completion
competion.temperature: what sampling temperature to use, between 0 and 2

image.prompt: a text description of the desired image(s). The maximum length is 1000 characters.
image.n: the number of images to generate. Must be between 1 and 10.
image.size: the size of the generated images
